  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
}

.signup-button:hover {
  background-color: #000000; /* Hover effect */
}
```

6. Click **Save**.

### **3. Inline CSS (Directly in the Page or Template)**
If you're editing a specific page or template, you can also place the CSS directly in the `<head>` section of that page.

1. Go to **Online Store** > **Themes**.
2. Click **Actions** > **Edit code**.
3. Locate the relevant template file under **Templates** or **Sections**. For example, it could be `page.liquid` or `custom-page.liquid`.
4. In the `<head>` section of the page, add the following `<style>` block:

```html
<style>
.email-signup-form {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 400px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

