.signup-button {
  background-color: #1c1c1c; /* Adjust to your theme */
  color: #fff;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 4px;
  font-size: 16px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
}

.signup-button:hover {
  background-color: #000000; /* Hover effect */
}
</style>
```

### **Recommendation**:
- For global styles, use **Option 2** (adding to `theme.css` or `theme.scss`).
- For specific page styles or testing, **Option 1** (theme customizer) or **Option 3** (inline CSS) may be faster and easier.

